## 3. Operators (you just practiced these)

```python
# Arithmetic:  +  -  *  /  //(floor)  %(remainder)  **(power)
# Comparison:  ==  !=  <  >  <=  >=        (chains: 3 < x < 10)
# Logical:     and  or  not    (return OPERANDS: 5 or 0 -> 5)
# Assignment:  =  +=  -=  *=  /=  //=  **=  %=
# Bitwise:     &  |  ^  ~  <<  >>
# Identity:    is   is not       (same object?)
# Membership:  in   not in       ("a" in "cat")
```

