## 10. Useful built-in functions

```python
abs(x)  round(x, 2)  pow(x, y)
min()  max()  sum()  sorted()  reversed()
len()  range()  enumerate()  zip()
map(func, lst)        # apply func to each
filter(func, lst)     # keep where func is True
any(iterable)   all(iterable)
isinstance(x, int)
int()  float()  str()  bool()  list()  dict()  set()  tuple()
ord("A")  # char -> code (65)
chr(65)   # code -> char ("A")
```

